        "The first cutpoint has an estimate of around 0, and they get progressively higher. How to make sense of this? Remember, we can interpret this on the latent normal distribution. Lets pull out the mean of each cutpoint, put them on a normal distribution, and compare it to the observed frequencies of the data:\n"
