        "This highlights the contentious interaction that attracted so much social media ire. Lets have this linear model make a prediction to understand the interaction a bit more, which we will also end up doing with a PyMC model. We'll estimate the feeling of cold for hypothetical individuals with ±1 SD on the clothes variable, and ±1 SD on the self objectivation variable. \n"
